o default text.\n\n- Example:\n\n```ts\nimport fullTextSearchPlugin from \"vuepress-plugin-full-text-search2\";\nexport default {\n  plugins: [\n    fullTextSearchPlugin({\n      locales: {\n        '/': {\n          placeholder: 'Search',\n        },\n        '/zh/': {\n          placeholder: '搜索',\n        },\n      },\n    }),\n  ],\n}\n```\n\n- Also see:\n  - [VuePress v2 - Guide > I18n]([../../guide/i18n.md](https://v2.vuepress.vuejs.org/guide/i18n.html))\n","readmeFilename":"README.md"}